{"tid":631713,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"新手寫故，跪求屌細力尐","createTime":"2018-04-16T17:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T04:43:27.000Z","uid":86146,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f47c3bd27811bdae6a4c959216278dffc6de1498","tid":631713,"uid":86146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T17:05:55.000Z","msg":"新手寫故，多多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌細力尐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n故事內容：雖然「我」今年只有24歲，但「我」已經令到過百個人死在我面前。<br />\n<br />\n正確來說，是已經處死過百個人。因為，「我」是一個行刑者。<br />\n<br />\n「我」的工作就是負責送死囚「上路」。面對一個個被「我」處死的死囚，對「我」來說他們只是為自己所做過的事負上責任。<br />\n<br />\n但「我」又有什麼資格逃避過殺人的罪行呢？難道殺死該死的人就不是殺人嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/articles/154002.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Farticles%2F154002.html&d=ZAqZwWIP7BgNGUp5wDsXYJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=8848f0cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/articles/154002.html</a>"},{"pid":"3f13309eb6a36ea5c8bbf13506ed675fd91cc090","tid":631713,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T01:05:10.000Z","msg":"尐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f80a30552174425f108392276f889f934e2cb56","tid":631713,"uid":86146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T14:20:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/articles/154002/154079.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Farticles%2F154002%2F154079.html&d=ZAqZwWIP7BgNGUp5wDsXYJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5ae8be1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/articles/154002/154079.html</a>"},{"p